\section{Abstract}
\label{sec:Abstract}
This document is a technical report about the ogre4j project hosted at 
Sourceforge.net. It covers the questions why this project exits, how it works, 
which alternatives are available in the open source universe and what are the 
future plans for it.

If you have any questions about this document or want to give us some feedback 
